用鉛筆畫個交叉<br />\n你就知足唔足料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d2587dc7f0c5dca1003b84ad15640ed8cda2b1","tid":914463,"uid":173260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d84c6f0362bb8b8ccb72b5d7542befdf5b561e2","tid":914463,"uid":71971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:46:51.000Z","msg":"撘單問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n600實呎3房1廁，全屋全新裝修，不連傢私<br />\n幾多錢左右先合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普通正正常常手工價位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nP.S改open kitchen 同會換窗<br />\nThanks 巴打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:58:58.000Z","msg":"巴打屋企人做裝修有地舖有興趣<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ko1145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fko1145&d=jvvzT6rx31Fn0FjFXWvslROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=69be6f1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ko1145</a>"},{"pid":"7ada2c4f936532e159e04215ea1b8b969a93b141","tid":914463,"uid":106356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T07:46:40.000Z","msg":"1.會唔會大價錢既料例如門等問佢拎個rate好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果自己買仲貴當然要佢包埋, 包埋當中唔岩位等風險<br />\n<br />\n2.磚唔包, 樓主諗住自購返屋俾佢裝?到時唔岩size同配合唔到裝法就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 磚牆包裝到頂?包唔包網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 油漆同防潮油如果知道邊隻, 會唔會買埋俾佢整工錢平少少<br />\n<br />\n4.門同門框加線如果唔同一間公司攪, 手尾可以好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5.地櫃石係裝修公司買石返黎現場cut包裝?<br />\n<br />\n6. 地台新做拋光磚呢個淨工價包唔包埋一開始清理至適合安裝磚既環境?(避免一入屋就話地台本身唔夠平做唔到而要加錢)<br />\n<br />\n7. 如果遲左幾多日會唔會有相應條約約束, 早而收貨既有冇獎金俾裝修公司?<br />\n<br />\n8. 包唔包日後跟手尾幾耐?<br />\n<br />\n9. 樓主跟workdone定工程日數俾錢?<br />\n<br />\n10. 喉包唔包去到配電位同去水位<br />\n<br />\n做咩工程都好最重要係白紙黑字寫清楚, 到時一句&quot;從來無講過包埋呢樣&quot;樓主就硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}